      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting. It has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather upholstery that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has a complete service history with a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of premium all-season tires with over 80% tread remaining. The engine runs smoothly with no leaks, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. While there are a few faint surface scratches near the trunk loading area, the car presents beautifully and drives like a dream. It is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next adventure.",
